<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="de">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Kein Patient ausgewählt — Digitale Behandlungsplanung</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script>
      tailwind.config = {
        theme: {
          extend: {
            colors: { klinik: { blue: "#1e40af" } },
          },
        },
      };
    </script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= basePath %>/style.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-50 font-sans text-slate-900 antialiased" style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif">
    <header class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-6">
        <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-klinik-blue">Digitale Behandlungsplanung</h1>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-amber-200 bg-amber-50 px-6 py-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg font-medium text-amber-900">Kein Patient ausgewählt</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-amber-800">
          Bitte öffnen Sie dieses Modul aus dem Kliniksystem mit einer gültigen Fallnummer
          (Parameter <code class="rounded bg-amber-100 px-1">fallnr</code> in der URL).
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
